e":"2020-02-08T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4572d26e97f04436a7802f0fe67d77994abc200e","tid":1869383,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13dfe9b0b5394ccc6143b98a227ec809b0332cb1","tid":1869383,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"無鳩啦啦又火炭又將軍澳開花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"火炭有幾冇啦啦 屋企隔離真係隔離營喎"},{"pid":"d6e1bd0fb22f5652efd7865168a85e5b84429352","tid":1869383,"uid":89974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4572d26e97f04436a7802f0fe67d77994abc200e","tid":1869383,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13dfe9b0b5394ccc6143b98a227ec809b0332cb1","tid":1869383,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"無鳩啦啦又火炭又將軍澳開花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"火炭有幾冇啦啦 屋企隔離真係隔離營喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"無啦啦唔係指行動原因<br />\n係指行動倉促<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年個個活動都有大量文宣，個個channel洗板一個禮拜以上，而家要去到附近嘅人睇直播先知有活動，咁樣唔叫無啦啦？"},{"pid":"5d552c601e57add0fb8407e322752e4cb2e67cf9","tid":1869383,"uid":191926,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"佢地有一個籍口<br />\n<br />\n就係 比一個星期黑警部署好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實係 <br />\n黑警班人型垃圾長期 mon住tg，連登<br />\n<br />\n再加上 香港大部份地點同垃圾站距離 都係&lt;15分鐘之內<br />\n<br />\n你早一日 同 早半日  根本分別不大<br />\n<br />\n雙方 呢種緊急開花<br />\n宣傳力度極差<br />\n無咩人知"},{"pid":"ee4fcd36a4ba44e55fe10ed19aaf7730c5135378","tid":1869383,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d552c601e57add0fb8407e322752e4cb2e67cf9","tid":1869383,"uid":191926,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"佢地有一個籍口<br />\n<br />\n就係 比一個星期黑警部署好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實係 <br />\n黑警班人型垃圾長期 mon住tg，連登<br />\n<br />\n再加上 香港大部份地點同垃圾站距離 都係&lt;1