問題，<br />\n你自問有無做過：<br />\n<br />\n呼籲住附近嘅朋友一齊落<br />\n呼籲同區人一齊加入<br />\n落街宣傳發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定係<br />\n<br />\n好嬲好嬲今晚一定要開花而家繼續好嬲先！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前者可以增加開花成功率，後者同白做係無分別"},{"pid":"d624987dd16dec248ec70f33a0ac997643d7a3f5","tid":1869383,"uid":29143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:40:33.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"fecdfb23fe364bd972fd27a2b37ad1c551ab1e75","tid":1869383,"uid":174607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"到有宣傳 又會話預約拘捕<br />\n講哂時間地點比班狗伏"},{"pid":"4fb40c07e7aedc0183e921b14e202416f435c6d5","tid":1869383,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50812f91a05a4eb43a25ab90e9bff3de0afdad49","tid":1869383,"uid":78085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6265951c89c7936068af327de3efa3e7d89d3525","tid":1869383,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T10:13:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb1067afea662fbadcfe4b9464557698141ab27c","tid":1869383,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fecdfb23fe364bd972fd27a2b37ad1c551ab1e75","tid":1869383,"uid":174607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"到有宣傳 又會話預約拘捕<br />\n講哂時間地點比班狗伏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"「我呼籲咗幾次，企最前嘅理應係和理非。大家被捕一樣會俾狗濫用武力，但一個告唔入，一個拉到就坐硬；一個極限都只係屌下狗，一個可以火燒狗肉，點解風險要後者食哂？<br />\n<br />\n和理非唔肯出，勇武一出嚟根本做唔到野就被人拉，風險收益比完全唔化算。」"},{"pid":"f705ff375f70b13b6ad159fea83c5b7c767f1524","tid":1869383,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df1abae56c2210016870bde2bb00eea93541db6c","tid":1869383,"uid":1856